    "description": {
      "value": "<p>To take this feature, you must have the <em><strong>Far Sight 1</strong></em> feature. When you use your Far Sight feature to change your visual point of origin, it now remains until your Junsugan ends and will maintain itself as long as you are within 90ft of it. You return to your normal visual senses (no action required), or you use Far Sight again.</p>",
